zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/orientationchange_event\"><code>orientationchange</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/pagehide_event\"><code>pagehide</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event\"><code>pageshow</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/paste_event\"><code>paste</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\"><code>popstate</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/rejectionhandled_event\"><code>rejectionhandled</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\"><code>storage</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/unhandledrejection_event\"><code>unhandledrejection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\"><code>unload</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplayactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayblur_event\"><code>vrdisplayblur</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplayconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydeactivate_event\"><code>vrdisplaydeactivate</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaydisconnect_event\"><code>vrdisplaydisconnect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplayfocus_event\"><code>vrdisplayfocus</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypointerunrestricted_event\"><code>vrdisplaypointerunrestricted</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/vrdisplaypresentchange_event\"><code>vrdisplaypresentchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":false,"content":"<p>当窗口即将被<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\" title=\"卸载（关闭）\"><code>卸载（关闭）</code></a>时,会触发该事件.此时页面文档依然可见,且该事件的默认动作可以被<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Event/preventDefault\" title=\"取消\"><code>取消</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">window.onbeforeunload = <var>funcRef</var></pre>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>funcRef</code> 是一个函数引用</li>\n <li>该函数应当将一个说明字符串赋值给<code>Event</code>对象的<code>returnValue</code>属性(兼容旧版浏览器),并且返回该字符串</li>\n <li>请注意,在Firefox4及其后续版本中,返回的说明字符串并不向用户显示,也就是无法自定义说明字符串.查看<a class=\"external link-https\" href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=588292\" rel=\" noopener\">Bug 588292</a>.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onbeforeunload</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  e <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>event<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 兼容IE8和Firefox 4之前的版本</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>e<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>returnValue <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'关闭提示'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Chrome, Safari, Firefox 4+, Opera 12+ , IE 9+</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">'关闭提示'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"附注","title":"附注","isH3":false,"content":"<p>当该事件返回的字符串（事前设置好的event.returnValue的值）不为null或者undefined时，弹出确认窗口让用户自行选择是否关闭当前页面。一些浏览器将该事件返回的字符串显示在弹出窗上。从Firefox 4、&nbsp;Chrome 51、Opera 38 和Safari 9.1开始，通用确认信息代替事件返回的字符串。比如，火狐上会显示“本页面要求您确认您要离开 - 您输入的数据可能不会被保存”，请查阅<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=588292\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;588292</a>和<a href=\"https://www.chromestatus.com/feature/5349061406228480\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Chrome Platform Status</a>。</p>\n\n<p>从2011年5月25日起,&nbsp; <a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html5-diff/#changes-2011-05-25\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5 规范</a> 声明:在该事件的处理函数中调用下列弹窗相关的方法时,可以忽略不执行,<code><a class=\"new\" href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/window.showModalDialog\">window.showModalDialog()</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/window.alert\">window.alert()</a></code>, <code><a class=\"new\" href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/window.confirm\">window.confirm()</a></code> <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/DOM/window.prompt\">window.prompt()</a></code>.</p>\n\n<p>需要指出的是，许多浏览器会忽略该事件并自动关闭页面无需用户的确认。火狐浏览器在配置页面<a>about:config</a>设有一个dom.disable_beforeunload的开关变量用于开启这个功能。</p>\n\n<p>你可以通过<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget/addEventListener\" title=\"window.addEventListener()\"><code>window.addEventListener()</code></a> 或者&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">beforeunload (en-US)</a></code> 创建该事件。更多信息请点击以上链接。</p>\n\n<p>创建这个事件能防止浏览器缓存部分由javascript产生的页面内容。在页面中含Javascript产生的内容情形下，再次导航返回到原页面javascript不在运行。如果事先有window.onbeforeunload事件，导航返回到先前的页面后javascript将被触发并更新页面内容。</p>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.WindowEventHandlers.onbeforeunload","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>该事件最初是由微软公司的IE4引进,虽然没有公开的规范说明,但所有浏览器都支持该事件.</code>目前已被添加至HTML5规范草案中.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"https://dev.w3.org/html5/spec-LC/history.html#unloading-documents\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5: Browsing the Web, Unloading documents</a><span title=\"Last Call\" style=\"color:#fff;background:#e2a669;display:inline-block; font-size:x-small; margin-left:6px; white-space:nowrap; padding:2px 5px;\">LC</span></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/zh-CN/library/ms536907(VS.85).aspx\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">MSDN: onbeforeunload event</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概述","id":"summary"},{"text":"语法","id":"syntax"},{"text":"示例","id":"example"},{"text":"附注","id":"附注"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"规范","id":"specification"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"当窗口即将被卸载（关闭）时,会触发该事件.此时页面文档依然可见,且该事件的默认动作可以被取消.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window.onbeforeunload","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onbeforeunload","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers.onbeforeunload","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/window/beforeunload_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/conflicting/web/api/window/beforeunload_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API","title":"指数"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window","title":"window.minimize"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event","title":"window.onbeforeunload"}],"pageTitle":"window.onbeforeunload | MDN","noIndexing":true}}